<div class="col clear facility">
<div class="col three-sm">
<h3 id="FacilityGroupProxy38812ac03cfb4f2ba06c302e810ef43e-7">Parking</h3>
<ul class="facility-list clear">
<li class="yes">Car Parking<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="no">Cycle parking<span class="hidden"> (no)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Disabled parking<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
</ul>
<div id="imageContent79e1baa9aacb45e0a1c8ad573563734d">
</div>
<p>Car parking is available on a Pay and Display basis. It applies to all cars parks and includes disabled areas. The cost is:</p>
<ul>
<li>Up to 30 minutes drop off Free </li>
<li>Up to two hours £2.70 </li>
<li>Between two and four hours £5.00 </li>
<li>Over four hours £6.50 </li>
</ul>
<p>There is a concession for long term patients/visitors of £2.50 for each and every 24hr period providing the visitor acquires a concessionary pass from either the security department or relevant ward and the pass is clearly displayed in the vehicle windscreen.</p>
